			<div class="content" id="post-content-2416026">
									

<p>While the first F-14 flew in 1970, it wasn't deployed by the Navy until '74; it's not impossible that there happened to be a squadron of F-111Bs available in 1971, as they weren't completely decommissioned until the F-14s came oneline.</p>

							</div>

								
					
